If you read the entire error message, you&#39;ll see it contains a hint:

&gt; error: type/value mismatch at argument 3 in template
&gt; parameter list for &#39;template&lt;class _Tp, class _Sequence, class _Compare&gt; class std::priority_queue&#39;
&gt; 
&gt; priority_queue &amp;lt; pair&amp;lt;double, int&amp;gt;, vector&amp;lt;pair&amp;lt;double, int&amp;gt;&amp;gt;, myComparator &amp;gt; pq;
&gt; 
